ute of Informatics|accessdate=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719225450/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=1990-582-16&lang=en|archive-date=2020-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>至於在本州最北端的[[青森縣|青森縣]]，有兩人在風災中受傷，82間房屋遭半毀。<ref name="DT24">{{cite report|first1=Kitamoto|last1=Asanobu|title=1990-575-13|url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=1990-575-13&lang=en|website=Digital Typhoon|publisher=National Institute of Informatics|accessdate=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718182834/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=1990-575-13&lang=en|archive-date=2020-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

